WEBVTT

00:02.095 --> 00:04.718
Last season on
<i>Falling Skies...</i>

00:06.304 --> 00:08.841
Alien structures
are going up over every city

00:08.842 --> 00:10.047
that we know about.

00:10.048 --> 00:12.812
They flew here in spaceships
and turned kids into slaves.

00:13.316 --> 00:14.667
What's happening to us?

00:15.350 --> 00:18.148
You really think you can
deal with those lizards?

00:19.052 --> 00:20.562
Skitters were our us too.

00:22.001 --> 00:23.845
Who do you think they are?

00:24.201 --> 00:25.468
I don't know.

00:25.524 --> 00:27.372
I wish we could use these
against them.

00:29.017 --> 00:31.171
We don't have enough people
 left for a suicide mission.

00:33.355 --> 00:35.185
The harness...
is a process.

00:35.416 --> 00:37.266
And Ben isn't free
from it.

00:37.332 --> 00:40.173
They'll call him back...
unless you go with them.

00:40.528 --> 00:41.950
You don't want to do this.

00:41.953 --> 00:43.654
No, I don't.

